text.tspan: Retrieve the public key of the wallet
signing key stored in Secure Enclave
Verify the signature of the wallet file
using the key stored in Secure Enclave
Perform PBKDF2 with salt and password,
then decrypt the encrypted private key
using AES256 with the derived key and IV
